01:02:36.660 --> 01:02:39.600
So to define a new type that you want to encode,

01:02:39.920 --> 01:02:43.380
you can add an encode hook, which takes in the instance

01:02:43.660 --> 01:02:46.080
and returns something that msgspec knows how to handle.

